# TechCorp npm configuration — VULNERABLE (misconfigured)
#
# BUG: @techcorp:registry should point to the INTERNAL registry.
# Instead it points to the attacker-controlled "public" registry.
# This is the misconfiguration that enables the dependency confusion attack.
#
# Attack: attacker publishes @techcorp/auth-lib@999.999.999 to this registry.
# npm resolves the highest available version and downloads the malicious package.
@techcorp:registry=http://localhost:4874/
